#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/for-maintainability/rust-specific/naming.md:3
msgid ""
"Follow Rust CamelCase and acronym capitalization (`camel-case-acronyms`)"
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/for-maintainability/rust-specific/naming.md:5
msgid ""
"Type names follow Rust's CamelCase convention. Acronyms are title-cased per "
"the Rust API Guidelines:"
msgstr ""

